that day will be canceled if you still need your remaining rides you must call to confirm those rides the office of accessible education and disgo reserve the right to refuse service canceling rides to cancel rides please call 650 725 2484 5 chug as soon as possible and leave a message parking accommodations up stanford's secure escort service 5 sure groups office of accessible education printer friendly version calendar search oae search oae information location & hours disgo cart service jobs at the oae office of accessible education 563 salvatierra walk stanford california 94305 650 723 1066 voice 650 725 5301 fax im oaegetinfo provide feedback copyright 2011 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints report a problem with this site
